\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104fbw1665702713269.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fbw1665702713269.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fbw1665702713269.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"fbw1665702713269\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      IncludeScript </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"fbw1665702713269__includescript_315391\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">An IncludeScript is a Development Object that defines a fragment of script that can be\n      inserted into ProcScript using the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#include</span> directive. </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fbw1665702713269__p_d96065e1_d96066e1_d96067e1\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tbm1665702708483.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tbm1665702708483.html\" title=\"IncludeScripts are fragments of ProcScript or JavaScript that are inserted into components during compilation.\">IncludeScripts</a>.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fbw1665702713269__topic_d64162e1_d64163e1_d64164e1_d64165e1_d64166e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1235604e66\"> Characteristics </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"fbw1665702713269__table_d10655e1_d10656e1_d10657e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fbw1665702713269__table_d10655e1_d10656e1_d10657e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fbw1665702713269__table_d10655e1_d10656e1_d10657e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbw1665702713269__table_d10655e1_d10656e1_d10657e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Icon:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbw1665702713269__table_d10655e1_d10656e1_d10657e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><img alt=\"Icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"fbw1665702713269__image_sct_kss_mwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/include_script.png?_LANG=enus\"/></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbw1665702713269__table_d10655e1_d10656e1_d10657e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbw1665702713269__table_d10655e1_d10656e1_d10657e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">inc</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbw1665702713269__table_d10655e1_d10656e1_d10657e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbw1665702713269__table_d10655e1_d10656e1_d10657e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbw1665702713269__table_d10655e1_d10656e1_d10657e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbw1665702713269__table_d10655e1_d10656e1_d10657e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hdr1665702713345.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hdr1665702713345.html\" title=\"An IncludeScript Library contains IncludeScript objects, which can be inserted into ProcScript using the #include directive and are resolved during compilation.\">IncludeScript Library</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbw1665702713269__table_d10655e1_d10656e1_d10657e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbw1665702713269__table_d10655e1_d10656e1_d10657e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbw1665702713269__table_d10655e1_d10656e1_d10657e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbw1665702713269__table_d10655e1_d10656e1_d10657e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ulo1665702550460.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ulo1665702550460.html\" title=\"A Uniface Development Object is an abstract data type that defines the characteristics and behavior of a logical application unit, such as a Component, Field, Message, Library, and so on.\">Development Object</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbw1665702713269__table_d10655e1_d10656e1_d10657e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbw1665702713269__table_d10655e1_d10656e1_d10657e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbw1665702713269__table_d10655e1_d10656e1_d10657e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbw1665702713269__table_d10655e1_d10656e1_d10657e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbw1665702713269__table_d10655e1_d10656e1_d10657e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fbw1665702713269__table_d10655e1_d10656e1_d10657e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">libinc:<var class=\"keyword varname\">LibraryName</var>/inc:<var class=\"keyword varname\">IncludeScript</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fbw1665702713269__topic_d64167e1_d64168e1_d64169e1_d64170e1_d64171e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1235604e275\"> Specialization </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fbw1665702713269__p_d96074e1_d96075e1_d96076e1\">IncludeScript specializes Development Object in the\n            following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fbw1665702713269__li_d38879e1_d38880e1_d38881e1\">It has an IncludeScript Library as parent. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fbw1665702713269__li_d38882e1_d38883e1_d38884e1\">It is used only during development, and has no\n               runtime equivalent. It is compiled into components when the components are compiled.\n            </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fbw1665702713269__p_d96077e1_d96078e1_d96079e1\">An IncludeScript can be inserted into ProcScript using\n            the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#include</span> instruction.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fbw1665702713269__p_d96080e1_d96081e1_d96082e1\">During compilation, the following IncludeScripts are\n            automatically included by the compiler without the need for an explicit\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#include</span> statement:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fbw1665702713269__li_d38885e1_d38886e1_d38887e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">SYSTEM_LIBRARY:DEFPARAM</code>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fbw1665702713269__li_d38888e1_d38889e1_d38890e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentLibrary</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">:DEFPARAM</code>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fbw1665702713269__p_d96083e1_d96084e1_d96085e1\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">DEFPARAM</code> IncludeScript is\n            intended to hold global constants.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fbw1665702713269__topic_d64172e1_d64173e1_d64174e1_d64175e1_d64176e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1235604e330\"> Properties </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fbw1665702713269__p_d96089e1_d96090e1_d96091e1\">Object Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fbw1665702713269__li_d38891e1_d38892e1_d38893e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrq1665702585385.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrq1665702585385.html\" title=\"Name of the development object, which uniquely identifies it.\">Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fbw1665702713269__li_d38894e1_d38895e1_d38896e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"owq1665702585461.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/owq1665702585461.html\" title=\"Type of Development Object. Read only.\">Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fbw1665702713269__li_d38897e1_d38898e1_d38899e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ybn1665702585544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ybn1665702585544.html\" title=\"Complete URI of the Development Object. Read only.\">Location</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fbw1665702713269__li_d38900e1_d38901e1_d38902e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fbw1665702713269__li_d38903e1_d38904e1_d38905e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ipc1665702585697.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ipc1665702585697.html\" title=\"Use this property to provide comments or instructions for the selected development object. You can use the toolbar and standard Windows keyboard shortcuts to format the text, copy and paste, and undo and redo edits.\">Documentation</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yah1665702621497.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>#include</a><p>Insert the contents of the specified IncludeScript in the location of the #include directive.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tbm1665702708483.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>IncludeScripts</a><p>IncludeScripts are fragments of ProcScript or JavaScript that are inserted into components during compilation.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612974\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612974\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "IncludeScript Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 IncludeScript An IncludeScript is a Development Object that defines a fragment of script that can be inserted into ProcScript using the #include directive. For more information, see IncludeScripts . Characteristics Characteristics Icon: Object type code: inc Main Development Object? No Part of: IncludeScript Library Contains: Property Generalization: Development Object Specializations: — Compilation Output: — URI format: libinc: LibraryName /inc: IncludeScript Specialization IncludeScript specializes Development Object in the following ways: It has an IncludeScript Library as parent. It is used only during development, and has no runtime equivalent. It is compiled into components when the components are compiled. An IncludeScript can be inserted into ProcScript using the #include instruction. During compilation, the following IncludeScripts are automatically included by the compiler without the need for an explicit #include statement: SYSTEM_LIBRARY:DEFPARAM ComponentLibrary :DEFPARAM The DEFPARAM IncludeScript is intended to hold global constants. Properties Object Properties: Name Type Location Description Documentation Related Links #include Insert the contents of the specified IncludeScript in the location of the #include directive. IncludeScripts IncludeScripts are fragments of ProcScript or JavaScript that are inserted into components during compilation. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}